## Summary
This documentation provides an overview of Amplitude Experiment, a behavior-driven experimentation platform that enables product teams to optimize user experiences through A/B testing, progressive feature delivery, and dynamic in-product experiences using feature flags that can be modified without changing code, with integration via SDKs or REST API.

